cats.name: Fluffy
cats.description: Ragdolls are known for their silky fur and bright blue eyes. They possess friendly, dog-like personalities and are often described as 'puppy-like' due to their tendency to follow their owners around and enjoy being held.

cats.name: Whiskers
cats.description: Persians are known for their luxurious coats and calm, affectionate personality. They thrive in peaceful environments and enjoy bonding closely with their owners, though they need regular grooming.

cats.name: Shadow
cats.description: Maine Coons are known as the 'gentle giants' of the cat world. They are large, friendly, and sociable, making them excellent companions for families with children and other pets.

cats.name: Luna
cats.description: Siamese cats are sleek and vocal, known for their striking blue eyes and short coat. They are intelligent, social, and thrive on attention and interaction, often engaging their humans in playful 'conversations'.
